Ranged=
[[Webweaver]] is the strongest weapon against Artio. Ideally you want to maximize range damage, while keeping your magic attack bonus at 0 or higher to allow for guaranteed freezes on Artio. Gear like [[bloodbark boots]], [[rune gloves]], [[god cape]] and [[ring of shadows]] are good to keep your magic bonus high enough, without sacrificing much range dps or incurring high risk. Defence bonus -- particularly magic defence -- is also beneficial for tanking [[PKers]].

