Magic=

Artio is significantly vulnerable to Magic. However, compared to Ranged, a Magic setup typically results in lesser defences which leaves the player more vulnerable to PKers.

It can be difficult to survive PKers if using magic equipment. Therefore, swapping out a protected item for [[Dinh's bulwark]] can aid in survivability; the player can simply switch to Dinh's if under attack. Bringing [[black dragonhide armour|black d'hide]] to switch to is also wise. Players using [[Tumeken's shadow]] can get away with wearing defensive ranged items like [[Masori_armour#Fortified_2|fortified masori]] or [[Armadyl armour|Armadyl]], if they have a high magic accuracy bonus (+100, or higher).

